{"tid":909174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德男跳傘失敗 15秒墮百米慘死","createTime":"2018-11-20T07:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T12:19:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"279e404fea2ef9b6af8e6e071d045abda58c5bc4","tid":909174,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】葡萄牙跳傘聖地納扎雷（Nazare），昨日發生一宗跳傘意外，一名50歲德國男子與好友挑戰懸崖跳傘，一躍而下時因降傘未能開啟，當場以時速160公里墮地慘死，他的隊友與其他民眾皆目睹他墮崖身亡的一刻。<br />\n據外媒報導，在當地時間19日中午時分，這名德國男子和隊友準備在一處懸崖跳傘。朋友的降傘成功打開並落地，但他的降傘並未如所料開啟，當場直接墮崖跌死。正準備跳崖的隊友們，目睹慘劇過程。有人在崖上大喊：「你還好嗎？」旁邊另外一名目擊女子則直呼：「我的天啊！」據悉墜崖男子隨即被送往醫院急救，但由於傷勢嚴重，宣告不治身亡。<br />\n警方表示，這名德國男子墮崖的高度約為95米，估計他墮崖時的速度約為時速160公里，撞擊力相當大。對於目擊這場死亡意外發生的所有朋友與民眾，警方也安排心理醫師進行治療與諮詢。<br />\n事發地點納札雷是著名的跳傘景點，衝浪也非常盛行，吸引很多挑戰極限運動者慕名前來，但先前也曾發生過跳傘死亡意外。在2013年7月，一名29歲瑞典男子也因為傘沒開，最後跳傘失敗墮崖慘死。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/w.n3P5h_SnITZcIY2odiqw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2018-11/547f0130-ec92-11e8-88fe-0a80a35570b5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fw.n3P5h_SnITZcIY2odiqw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-11%2F547f0130-ec92-11e8-88fe-0a80a35570b5&h=a460e7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子跳傘失敗，隊友拍下他墮崖慘死瞬間。（網圖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%85%8E%E5%85%A5-%E5%BE%B7%E7%94%B7%E8%B7%B3%E5%82%98%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-15%E7%A7%92%E5%A2%AE%E7%99%BE%E7%B1%B3%E6%85%98%E6%AD%BB-045200841.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2585%258E%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E5%2582%2598%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597-15%25E7%25A7%2592%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E6%2585%2598%25E6%25AD%25BB-045200841.html&d=GLHxB1Bl6fk81vWTn2Ta6wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=98b0363d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%85%8E%E5%85%A5-%E5%BE%B7%E7%94%B7%E8%B7%B3%E5%82%98%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-15%E7%A7%92%E5%A2%AE%E7%99%BE%E7%B1%B3%E6%85%98%E6%AD%BB-045200841.html</a>"},{"pid":"6f7c4629b899e709db40162f1e747e8616cf7d43","tid":909174,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"肉醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ee8988287e68bf2cdbd8f0309ceb214c70e570","tid":909174,"uid":52511,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"得95米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22395c6e48aef86c149e5a195d49d614b347f79","tid":909174,"uid":33206,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"有人在崖上大喊：「你還好嗎？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2857ce760b66d1f5063ae040e0355843832dfb08","tid":909174,"uid":14065,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"c22395c6e48aef86c149e5a195d49d614b347f79","tid":909174,"uid":33206,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"有人在崖上大喊：「你還好嗎？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:16:39.000Z","msg":"係囉點解德國佬識中文"},{"pid":"66f2e411425bcefb6beeece0e7d741742d6cf273","tid":909174,"uid":69213,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc8f94b0d27e59aa50759a3f59ab0bcc330411f7","tid":909174,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"有無片"},{"pid":"4e1a19b9b628030bbf15d3c09b6dc1b786990671","tid":909174,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-2